Pre Penetration Testing Checklist

Gather information about client organization
	- Foundation
	- Objectives of the company
	- Products
	- Employee information (Stakeholders / IT admin)
	- Business partners
	- Clients

Visit the Client organization premises
	- Network Equipment
	- Server room
	
List key personnel contact details of client
	- Name
	- Department
	- Role
	- Mobile / Office number
	- Email
	
Identify office space / location

Obtain temp id card

Ask the client to create domain accounts

Ask the previous penetration testing reports

Identify client security compliance requirements

Ask the list of servers, OS and Network devices

Hire a lawyer

Prepare legal penetration testing document

Propare non disclosure agreement

Obtain a liability insurance

Allocate a budget for the project

List the timescale

Daily / Hourly fees negotiation

Time line for the project 

Draft the cost for the project

Discuss the test workflow

Discuss the final report
